{"tid":2330645,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金世正大展全方位才華　週末推出《驅魔麵館》最新 OST！","createTime":"2020-12-18T07:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:51:59.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbc6b528f51e60dab54c62fdcac06961b57c8d5","tid":2330645,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_9f9e941a65a1b8db2a2dd9c4095f73ce/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-18/132421-889482.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_9f9e941a65a1b8db2a2dd9c4095f73ce%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-18%2F132421-889482.png&h=973ea941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在《驅魔麵館》中飾演「都哈娜」的金世正不只演技大獲好評，接下來還將推出參與創作的 OST，不禁讓人感嘆「世正到底有什麼不會的」？<br />\n<br />\nOCN 週末劇《驅魔麵館》製作單位今天透露，金世正將演唱劇中的第二首 OST「再會」，並於 20 日傍晚公開正式音源。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_49f614e670e201ee2b24bb945e9fa83d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-18/132421-889479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_49f614e670e201ee2b24bb945e9fa83d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-18%2F132421-889479.jpg&h=5d66a376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「再會」以金世正特有的感性歌聲淡淡地詮釋情感，配上氛圍神秘的編曲，帶來令人印象深刻的感動。特別的是，金世正還融入身為主演的體悟，親自參與了「再會」的作詞、作曲乃至編曲工作。<br />\n<br />\n金世正將於韓國時間 20 日發表「再會」，這週末除了要準時收聽新歌外，也別忘了鎖定播出！"},{"pid":"3a8c669d2041fe70047cc26eabd8edcb3ff7a59a","tid":2330645,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"正正正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}